{
  "stem": "7598.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at that point, I had them telephone my parents, who by then knew we were in Portugal and were expecting us, and seeing it's at Primrose 2410.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother said, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, you can collect your daughter Odette at Paddington Station tonight at 10 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the next thing I heard was-- because my English was not terribly good-- are you there, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Rubinstein?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think it was all just a bit too much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, my brother seemed in great control.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wasn't all that worried, because they explained to us that an internment camp was not a concentration camp, but somehow he would be useful to Britain, be able to give them more information.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, my parents arrived at the station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father, who looked 20 years older than he did two years ago, seemed like a white ghost.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't say very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We just hugged, didn't say very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And went to the [INAUDIBLE] court and I went to bed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And during that night, my father came and touched me just to see whether I was really there or whether it was a dream.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was on a Thursday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm not quite sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I think it was around the 10th.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My parents were very anxious to visit my brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I don't quite know how they made all the necessary inquiries, but we were told that on the Saturday we would be able to go to the internment camp, which wasn't very far from London, and we were to visit him.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, in fact, by the Monday he was released.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will tell you in a moment.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
